---
// PromoHighlight - Destaque do plano promocional como incentivo secundário
---

<section class="promo-section" id="oferta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-badge">Oferta Especial</span>
      <h2>Plano exclusivo para novos alunos</h2>
      <p>Após sua aula experimental, aproveite condições especiais para começar</p>
    </div>

    <div class="promo-grid">
      <div class="promo-card reveal">
        <div class="promo-card-header">
          <span class="promo-tag">Starter 300 pontos</span>
          <div class="promo-price-block">
            <span class="currency">R$</span>
            <span class="price">140</span>
            <span class="period">/mês</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="promo-card-body">
          <div class="promo-breakdown">
            <div class="breakdown-item">
              <div class="breakdown-icon points">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                  <path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="breakdown-info">
                <span class="breakdown-value">300 pontos</span>
                <span class="breakdown-label">= 6 aulas/mês com professores 50+ pts</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="breakdown-plus">+</div>

            <div class="breakdown-item bonus">
              <div class="breakdown-icon tickets">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M20 12v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6"/>
                  <path d="M4 8V6a2 2 0 012-2h12a2 2 0 012 2v2"/>
                  <rect x="2" y="8" width="20" height="4" rx="1"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="breakdown-info">
                <span class="breakdown-value">24 tickets/mês</span>
                <span class="breakdown-label">nos 3 primeiros meses</span>
                <span class="breakdown-detail">Para professores de 5, 25 ou 40 pts</span>
                <span class="breakdown-bonus">Bônus incluído!</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="promo-total">
            <div class="total-line">
              <span class="total-label">Total nos 3 primeiros meses</span>
              <span class="total-value">até 30 aulas/mês</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-line highlight">
              <span class="total-label">Preço por aula</span>
              <span class="total-value accent">R$ 4,67</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <ul class="promo-features">
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Aulas de 25 minutos ao vivo
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Professores certificados TESOL
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Disponível 24h, 7 dias por semana
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Cancele quando quiser
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="promo-cta-note">
            <p>Disponível após sua primeira aula experimental</p>
          </div>

          <a href="#lead-form" class="btn-lp promo-cta">
            Quero Experimentar
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="promo-benefits reveal">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Conversação real</h3>
          <p>Pratique falar inglês de verdade com um professor dedicado a cada aula.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
              <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Flexibilidade total</h3>
          <p>Escolha horários que cabem na sua rotina e estude quando for melhor para você.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"/>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Professores dedicados</h3>
          <p>Mais de 1.300 professores certificados prontos para te acompanhar.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .promo-section {
    padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
  }

  .section-header { text-align: center; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto 3rem; }
  .section-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 0.375rem 1rem; font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary); background: var(--color-primary-subtle); border-radius: var(--radius-full); margin-bottom: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .section-header h2 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .section-header p { font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--color-gray-600); }

  .promo-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; align-items: start; }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .promo-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; } }

  .promo-card { background: white; border-radius: var(--radius-xl); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); overflow: hidden; border: 2px solid var(--color-primary); }
  .promo-card-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, #0e7490 100%); padding: 1.5rem; color: white; text-align: center; }
  .promo-tag { display: inline-block; padding: 0.375rem 1rem; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); border-radius: var(--radius-full); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .promo-price-block { display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: center; gap: 0.25rem; }
  .currency { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; opacity: 0.9; }
  .price { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; }
  .period { font-size: 1.25rem; opacity: 0.9; }
  .promo-card-body { padding: 1.5rem; }

  .promo-breakdown { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--color-gray-50); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .breakdown-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; width: 100%; }
  .breakdown-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: var(--radius-md); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .breakdown-icon.points { background: var(--color-primary-subtle); color: var(--color-primary); }
  .breakdown-icon.tickets { background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.15); color: #b45309; }
  .breakdown-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .breakdown-value { font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-dark); }
  .breakdown-label { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-gray-600); }
  .breakdown-detail { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-gray-500); font-style: italic; }
  .breakdown-bonus { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .breakdown-plus { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-gray-400); }
  .breakdown-item.bonus { background: rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.05); padding: 0.75rem; border-radius: var(--radius-md); border: 1px dashed var(--color-primary); }

  .promo-total { border-top: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200); padding-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .total-line { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0.5rem 0; }
  .total-label { color: var(--color-gray-600); }
  .total-value { font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-dark); }
  .total-line.highlight { background: rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.08); margin: 0 -0.5rem; padding: 0.75rem 0.5rem; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); }
  .total-value.accent { color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.25rem; }

  .promo-features { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .promo-features li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0; color: var(--color-gray-700); }
  .promo-features li svg { color: var(--color-primary); flex-shrink: 0; }

  .promo-cta-note { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .promo-cta-note p { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-gray-500); font-style: italic; }
  .promo-cta { width: 100%; }

  .promo-benefits { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .benefit-card { background: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); transition: all var(--transition-base); }
  .benefit-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .benefit-icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: var(--color-primary-subtle); color: var(--color-primary); border-radius: var(--radius-md); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .benefit-card h3 { font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .benefit-card p { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-gray-600); line-height: 1.5; }

  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: all 0.6s ease; }
  .reveal.is-visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
</style>
